                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Utilize Existing Cameras</h3>
                        <p>We integrate with your property's existing camera infrastructure to monitor vehicle and pedestrian movements throughout your entire property.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step" data-step="2">
